textAfterTable: Upcoming Events: - All - Athletics Fine Arts Lectures & Presentations Other August 2015 02 Sunday 6:30 PM Family-Friendly Fun at Denison The Granville Recreation District presents Bob Piascik and friends with an interactive show for all ages at Denison Show Event Details Full Description: Veteran Columbus performing artist Bob Piascik has assembled four fellow musicians (and fellow parents) to create an interactive show that is totally family-friendly. Featuring favorite modern hits from Hannah Montana, the Cheetah Girls, Aly and A.J., Ashley Tisdale, the Jonas Brothers, Smashmouth, Aaron Carter and more, featured along with music that emphasizes positive values. Join the fun with lots of audience interaction, community sing-along, and dancing at this high-energy event. Also featured will be the Steamroller Bagel food truck. Address: Fine Arts Quad, Denison University, 240
